oxicity or dwell on the perceived destructive impact of toxic leaders, successful companies come up with resourceful, innovative strategies for turning seeming deficits into opportunities.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 25. Nov 2020) 0aExecutive ability. 0aExecutivesxPsychology. 0aLeadership. 0aManagement. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Leadership.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311070420440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080477257040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804772570423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780804772570.jpg  a978-3-11-070420-4  SUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles